---
import Layout from "../layouts/index.astro";
import ModeToggle from "../components/mode-toggle";
---

<Layout>
  <div
    class="text-foreground relative z-10 mx-auto my-6 w-full max-w-prose px-6 text-left font-normal sm:max-w-2xl sm:px-8 md:my-8 md:max-w-3xl lg:my-20 lg:max-w-4xl lg:px-6 xl:my-16 xl:max-w-4xl xl:px-4"
    data-reading-surface
  >
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 tracking-[0.2em]">
      <h1
        class="mb-4 text-left text-2xl font-bold sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl"
      >
        Meet me, Yusoof Moh
      </h1>
    </div>
    <div
      class="my-0 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-1 tracking-[0.2em]"
    >
      <ModeToggle client:load />
    </div>
    <div
      data-mode="full"
      class="mt-2 text-[0.9375rem] sm:text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl xl:text-lg"
    >
      <div class="typeset typeset-portfolio">
        <p>
          In the name of Allah, and by His grace. My name is pronounced <i
            >yu-soof</i
          >. I&rsquo;m a Malang-based <strong
            >full-stack and platform engineer</strong
          > delivering TypeScript applications, data workflows, CI/CD, Kubernetes
          migrations, and production reliability improvements.
        </p>

        <h2>What I do</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Applications and data:</strong> TypeScript, React, TanStack,
            Node.js, Hono, NestJS, Astro, PostgreSQL, and migration workflows.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Platforms and delivery:</strong> Docker, Kubernetes, Amazon EKS,
            Helm, Argo CD, GitHub Actions, Kafka, Cloudflare Workers, and R2.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Quality and operations:</strong> Vitest, Playwright,
            OpenTelemetry, Grafana, Loki, Tempo, Prometheus, staged rollouts, and
            root-cause analysis.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Selected work</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>NADI:</strong> Migrated a payment workflow to DOKU and helped
            improve reported transaction success from 60% to 95% over three months.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>YDSF.org:</strong> Modernized donation, verification, analytics,
            export, authentication, and database-migration workflows.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>ElectGo / Tai Sin Group:</strong> Migrated <strong
              >seven production PIM deployments</strong
            > and <strong>300+ n8n workflows</strong> to Amazon EKS through verified
            infrastructure and application cutovers.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Beyond work</h2>
        <p>
          I cultivate edamame, enjoy regional motorcycle tours, and keep a steady
          habit of deep research. I base my understanding of Islam on the first three
          generations of the ummah, focusing on <strong>tawhid</strong> and <strong
            >tafsir</strong
          >. I conduct <i>tahsin</i> classes and support local communities.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Open to meaningful remote or contract collaborations.</strong>
          Reach me via
          <a href="mailto:me@yusoofsh.id" onclick="sa_event('email_clicked')"
            >Mail</a
          > /
          <a href="/twitter" onclick="sa_event('twitter_clicked')">Twitter</a> /
          <a href="/linkedin" onclick="sa_event('linkedin_clicked')">LinkedIn</a>
          /
          <a href="/github" onclick="sa_event('github_clicked')">GitHub</a>. May
          Allah bless our endeavors and lead us to His everlasting mercy.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      data-mode="tldr"
      class="mt-2 text-[0.9375rem] sm:text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl xl:text-lg"
    >
      <div class="typeset typeset-portfolio">
        <p>
          Bismillah. I&rsquo;m a Malang-based <strong
            >full-stack and platform engineer</strong
          > working across TypeScript applications, data workflows, CI/CD,
          Kubernetes, and production reliability.
        </p>
        <h2>Recent highlights</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Improved NADI payment reliability through a DOKU migration.</li>
          <li>Modernized YDSF.org&rsquo;s donation-platform workflows.</li>
          <li>
            Migrated <strong>seven production PIM deployments</strong> and <strong
              >300+ n8n workflows</strong
            > to Amazon EKS.
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          I use structured AI-assisted workflows with explicit tests and runtime
          verification. <strong
            >Open to meaningful remote or contract collaborations.</strong
          > Reach me via
          <a href="mailto:me@yusoofsh.id" onclick="sa_event('email_clicked')"
            >Mail</a
          > /
          <a href="/twitter" onclick="sa_event('twitter_clicked')">Twitter</a> /
          <a href="/linkedin" onclick="sa_event('linkedin_clicked')">LinkedIn</a>
          /
          <a href="/github" onclick="sa_event('github_clicked')">GitHub</a>.
          Baarakallahu fiik.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
